title: While Peyton struggles, Denver 'D' keeps Broncos in the game (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,466 While Peyton struggles, Denver 'D' keeps Broncos in the game (Yahoo Sports) Not so long ago, Peyton Manning had the Denver Broncos offense scoring at a record-setting clip. Six games into the season, the Broncos 'D' is drawing some comparisons, however preliminary, to some of the best. A more apt comparison might be the 2000 Ravens, whose top-ranked defense propped up an offense that often went nowhere.
